         <div id="phishingandspam" class="content"> 
          <p>Phishing refers to an email that attempts to fraudulently acquire personal information from you, such as your Apple ID, password and/or credit card information. On the surface, the email may appear to be from a legitimate company or individual, but it's not.</p> 
          <p>Please refer to <a href="/legal/more-resources/phishing/">http://www.apple.com/legal/more-resources/phishing/</a> for more information and resources, including how to report suspicious emails.</p> 
